  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あなたが寝坊して
船を出してくれなかったせいで
頼まれたホットドッグが買えなかったよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The boat already left because you slept in so late!
I couldn't get the hotdog he asked me for!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どうしてくれるのさ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are we gonna do now?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おい、お前！
俺が乗るはずだった船を
出航させないなんて、どういうつもりだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, you! What do you mean the boat I
was supposed to get on already set out?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>俺を誰だと思ってんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who do you think I am?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……知るか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...As if I know.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クーリッジ！
お前の寝坊で船を逃した相手に対して
それはあまりにも失礼だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Coolidge! That's extremely rude behavior
toward someone who missed their ship
because you overslept.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>てめぇ……許せねぇ！
痛い目見してやっからな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why you... No way am I gonna let this slide!
I'm gonna show you a world of hurt for that!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ほ、ホットドッグの
責任とってもらうからね！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I'm gonna have to make you
take responsiblity for that hotdog!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
